bibl.seg: KROMANN Anne, Alaxandrinerne hos Ramus. Avec résumé en anglais: The Alexandrian Coins in Ramus's Catalogue.
NNF-Nytt. Meddelelser fra Norsk Numismatik Forening 1992, No. 2, pp. 45-52, ill.

The early acquisitions of the Copnehage Coins Cabinet were made after 1799 thanks to te efforts of Chr. Ramus, who wrote the first printed catalogue of it (published in 1916). - Non vidimus. Cf. NL 129 (1993) p. 28, No. 185.
